  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered, middle-aged human with brown eyes set under heavy lids and a square, workingman’s jaw. Black hair is kept in a plain, close arrangement that leaves a high hairline and pronounced brow ridge exposed. Light skin shows permanent sun-freckling across the nose and cheeks, with thickened, callused hands typical of long service behind a bar. The voice is steady and practiced, carrying the controlled cadence of someone accustomed to managing crowds and disputes without escalation.",
